{"id": "1184004771171012621", "channel_id": "1184004771171012621", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "很抱歉，各位。我有一件事想跟大家提前溝通：我們想要暫時關閉並重新優化第五章內容，待 12 月 27 日再重新開放。\n\n因為我們希望主線章節代表著整個遊戲各方面最高的質量水準，能帶給大家與前面的章節一致、甚至是更優秀的體驗，然而很遺憾當前的第五章我們認為沒有達到這樣的目標，我們希望能使之回到基準線上。\n\n這有多方面的原因構成：嘗試了可能並不適合我們遊戲的敘事手法，代入視角，未及時將極夜測試與破曉測試吸收的玩法設計、故事設計經驗傳承至第五章……其中最根本的還是校貓我本人對此的大意與僥倖心態，未在開發計劃中為團隊成員留出足夠的配合打磨時間。為此，我向大家鄭重道歉，並承諾未來我們會吸取教訓不會再發生類似的事情。\n如果暫時關閉，我們會以公平為原則妥善處理進度、獎勵、密契與鑰令獎勵。遊戲內容方面也會在有其他支線關卡來供大家繼續遊玩，也會強化主線困難模式、輪轉間隙的獎勵讓大家有更多其他遊玩目標。\n\n重新調整第五章的計劃必然有很多的困難和挑戰。但之所以還是想要這麼做，是因為我們非常希望能夠讓大家作為守密人，留下一個全方面都更好的第五章回憶。我們非常清楚，這會給大家帶來很多困惑、疑問和擔憂，也可能有很多更好的意見要表達。為此，校貓在這裡想要聽聽大家的想法，拜托請全部告訴我吧，我會盡力與大家一起探討更好的方案。", "timestamp": "2023-12-12T05:32:15.192000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 46}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184004771171012621", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅我們請求重新調整第五章", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1184005831889522748", "channel_id": "1184004771171012621", "type": 0, "author_id": "194426817908703232", "author_name": ".oaq", "author_bot": false, "content": "加油!", "timestamp": "2023-12-12T05:36:28.087000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184004771171012621", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅我們請求重新調整第五章", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1184005956934307870", "channel_id": "1184004771171012621", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "I apologize, everyone. There’s something I want to communicate in advance: We plan to temporarily close and revamp the content of Chapter 5, aiming to reopen it on December 27th.\n\nWe aspire for the main story chapters to represent the highest quality aspect of the entire game, to provide an experience consistent with, or even better than, the previous chapters. Regrettably, we feel that the current Chapter 5 has not met these goals and we aim to bring it back up to our standard.\n\nThere are multiple reasons contributing to this decision: the employment of narrative techniques that may not suit our game, perspective immersion, and the failure to incorporate gameplay and story design experiences learned from the extreme night and dawn tests into Chapter 5... But most fundamentally, it is my own negligence and wishful thinking that did not allocate enough time for the development team to properly polish the game. For this, I offer my sincere apologies and vow that we will learn from this lesson to prevent similar issues in the future.\n\nIf we temporarily close, we will handle progress, rewards, and keys given out for pledges according to the principle of fairness. We will also continue to provide alternative side mission content for everyone to enjoy, as well as enhancing the rewards for the main storyline’s hard mode and interim rotation periods, giving everyone more gameplay goals.\n\nThere will inevitably be many difficulties and challenges in readjusting the plan for Chapter 5. However, we still wish to proceed because we hope to provide an all-around better memory of Chapter 5 for everyone as part of the secret-keeping community. We understand that this will cause confusion, raise questions, and concerns, and there may be much better suggestions to be expressed. For this reason, I’d like to hear your thoughts. Please do share them all with me, and I will do my best to discuss and explore better solutions together with everyone.", "timestamp": "2023-12-12T05:36:57.900000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184004771171012621", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅我們請求重新調整第五章", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
